title: William Azanor
text: William Azanor (born 28 June 1959) is a Nigerian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201980%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Featherweight">men's featherweight</a> event at the <a href="1980%20Summer%20Olympics">1980 Summer Olympics</a>.
